<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Alcohol Ordering</title>
<style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #000000;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #8eb50b;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 1em;
        }

        .menu-item {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 1em;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .menu-item img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .cart {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 1em;
            position: fixed;
            right: 1em;
            top: 1em;
            max-width: 300px;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 999;
        }

        .cart-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #8eb50b;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Alcohol Menu</h1>
    </header>

    <section id="menu">
        <!-- Alcohol items will be dynamically added here using JavaScript -->
    </section>

    <div class="cart" id="cart">
        <h2>Shopping Cart</h2>
        <div id="cart-items">
            <!-- Cart items will be dynamically added here using JavaScript -->
        </div>
        <p>Total: &#8377<span id="total">0.00</span></p>
        <button onclick="checkout()">Checkout</button>
    </div>
<footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 Alcohol Ordering</p>
    </footer>
<script>
        // Sample alcohol menu data
        const alcoholMenuData = [
            { id: 11, name: 'Whiskey', description: 'Aged whiskey with a rich and smoky flavor.', price: 25.99, imageUrl: 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQmu9zInuwl4SbPOjbO34pk_YEmRZHKrZ9krw&usqp=CAU' },
            { id: 12, name: 'Vodka', description: 'Premium vodka distilled for a smooth taste.', price: 19.99, imageUrl: 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcR9wxcgPM8vuEl1j-P-9VyJcHZ5-hpQnhdCEQ&usqp=CAU' },
            { id: 13, name: 'Red Wine', description: 'A classic red wine with deep, fruity notes.', price: 15.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
            { id: 14, name: 'Craft Beer', description: 'Locally brewed craft beer with a variety of flavors.', price: 8.99, imageUrl: 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQxoP5thsj4VEyKg9Q0lTSh4GGYmIRpd_YXPQ&usqp=CAU' },
            { id: 15, name: 'Tequila', description: 'High-quality tequila for a perfect shot or cocktail.', price: 29.99, imageUrl: 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTA_Cj6EEJ8L5XT6iZXKfW51BJgssnI96FmqQ&usqp=CAU' },
            { id: 16, name: 'Gin', description: 'Classic gin with botanical flavors for a refreshing cocktail.', price: 21.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
            { id: 17, name: 'Chardonnay', description: 'Crisp and buttery Chardonnay with hints of citrus.', price: 18.99, imageUrl: 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS6TlODjH4h-gfpmeXyqBt4E25au5XqInQl5g&usqp=CAU' },
            { id: 18, name: 'Rum', description: 'Smooth and versatile rum for mixing your favorite cocktails.', price: 23.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
            { id: 19, name: 'Prosecco', description: 'Bubbly and delightful Prosecco for celebrations.', price: 16.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
            { id: 20, name: 'Cognac', description: 'Premium cognac with rich and complex flavors.', price: 34.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
        ];
// Initialize alcohol menu and cart
        const menuSection = document.getElementById('menu');
        const cartItemsContainer = document.getElementById('cart-items');
        const totalElement = document.getElementById('total');
        let cart = [];

        // Add alcohol items dynamically
        alcoholMenuData.forEach(item => {
            const menuItem = document.createElement('div');
            menuItem.classList.add('menu-item');
            menuItem.innerHTML = `
                <img src="${item.imageUrl}" alt="${item.name}">
                <h2>${item.name}</h2>
                <p>${item.description}</p>
                <p> &#8377 ${item.price.toFixed(2)}</p>
                <button onclick="addToCart(${item.id})">Add to Cart</button>
            `;
            menuSection.appendChild(menuItem);
        });

        // Add item to cart
        function addToCart(itemId) {
            const selectedItem = alcoholMenuData.find(item => item.id === itemId);
            cart.push(selectedItem);
            updateCart();
        }

        // Update cart display
        function updateCart() {
            cartItemsContainer.innerHTML = '';
            let total = 0;

            cart.forEach(item => {
                const cartItem = document.createElement('div');
                cartItem.classList.add('cart-item');
                cartItem.innerHTML = `
                    <p>${item.name}</p>
                    <p> &#8377 ${item.price.toFixed(2)}</p>
                `;
                cartItemsContainer.appendChild(cartItem);
                total += item.price;
            });

            totalElement.textContent = total.toFixed(2);
        }

        // Checkout function (you can customize this function)
        function checkout() {
            alert('Checkout function triggered!');
            // Add your checkout logic here
        }
    </script>
